→ Data Analytics & AI: Industrial facilities and infrastruc- tures are generating ever-growing amounts of data. Using methods of machine-based data analysis and artificial intelligence (AI), we help operators increase availability, improve operational quality, and reduce the stress on humans and the environment. At the same time, our quality statement on industrial-grade AI expresses its trustworthiness, reliability, and robustness according to the requirements suggested for the European Union’s upcoming AI Act.